v0.3.0 2022-09-16T03:38:25Z

    - use faster random number generator

v0.2.0 2022-06-19T08:48:05Z

    - add method to_s() to Word/Name/Address
    - add arg separater to Name#kanji/hiragana/katakana/romaji
    - del the way to call constructor with keyword args. 

v0.1.1 2022-06-02T03:04:17Z

    - update cpanfile
    - format by perltidy

v0.1.0 2022-05-24T20:07:31Z

    - change OO systems Moo -> Class::Tiny
    - organize modules
    - update cpanfile
    - use VERSION instead of use feature.
    - rename first_name -> given, last_name -> family
    - introduce Data::Gimei::Random
    - delete Data::Gimei::random()

v0.0.7 2022-05-06T05:47:29Z

